ription. The only result that will change significantly is FCs. We will probably get similar DE genes with roughly double FCs. If we add an option to output shrunk FCs (i.e. results of `lfcShrink`) then we might get similar results to our previous version with `betaPrior = True`. I have to test this outside Galaxy. If no one else is eager to do this test, I can do this next week :)","files":null}]}